==English==
===Noun===
'''tessellation''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]''; ''plural'' '''tessellations''')

#(''uncountable'') The property or fact of [[tessellate|tessellating]].
#:''Squares can be used for tessellation.''
#(''countable'') The result of tessellating an area or plane.
#:''This is a tessellation of the plane with squares and regular octagons.''
#(''uncountable'') A less common name for [[polygon tessellation]].

